OL,5, An advert for Blackpool Pleasure       
OL,6, Beach's Halloween event has been banned
OL,7, after the advertising watchdog ruled it
OL,8, was "likely to distress" children.     
OL,10,FThe Advertising Standards Authority    
OL,11,F(ASA) upheld 26 complaints about the   
OL,12,Fposter, which showed a pale face, with 
OL,13,Fyellow eyes and bloodied teeth, and the
OL,14,Ftext "Journey to Hell Freak Nights".   
OL,16,FIt said the complainants believed it   
OL,17,Fwas "inappropriate and disturbing".    
OL,19,FBlackpool Pleasure Beach said it would 
OL,20,Ffollow the ASA's recommendations.      
